Product Description

Nina Ricci is a famous fashion house founded in Paris and is especially known for bringing a feminine refined and romantic feel to its collections. Offering clothing accessories and perfumes which are the epitome of elegance this brand is renowned world over as it relates to fashionable folk of different ages. Start your day with the fruity fragrance of Nina Ricci Nina Eau De Toilette for women. An ideal choice for daily use the perfume is suited for young women thanks to its contemporary appeal. The perfume comes in a fairytale designed bottle that is as attractive as the scent. The top notes of this perfume include lime and lemon giving it a spontaneous and energetic feel. Complementing the citrus scent are middle notes of vanilla praline and candied apple that gives it caramel sweet hint reminding you of younger days at a carnival. With base notes of balmy musk white cedar and apple tree that give the fragrance a soft sensual aroma making it a perfect choice for everyday wear.
